Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.50,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.99,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,Why did a powered suit from \NYggdrasil suddenly appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.64,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a player?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.74,Main,Shalltear,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Knight and Death Warrior \Nwere destroyed so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.52,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. Just as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:29.00,Main,Cocytus,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Cocytus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.76,Main,Shalltear,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! I understand now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:39.39,Main,Shalltear,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Ains was expecting the \None in red armor to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:44.48,Main,Shalltear,0000,0000,0000,,He chose to send fewer soldiers in order \Nto lure the enemy out into the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:48.45,Main,Demiurge,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deduction from the \Ntwo of you, as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.28,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.68,Main,Aura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:59.53,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,He's from Drop of Red, one of the \Nthree adamantite teams in the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:03.16,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,It's reported that his team normally works \Nin the northern region of the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.29,Main,Mare,0000,0000,0000,,S-So that's why Lord Ains set \Na trap in this northern city!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.74,Main,Cocytus,0000,0000,0000,,So, he's a fish that took the bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.55,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:20.32,Main,Demiurge,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've achieved your original goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:24.31,Main,Demiurge,0000,0000,0000,,we should send stronger forces to \Nthat town and raze it to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.85,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that sounds good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:32.37,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I was thinking of \Nchanging the plans a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.95,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,and bringing the royal capital \Nto ruin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:42.20,Main,Demiurge,0000,0000,0000,,If that is what you wish, we will simply obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.15,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.85,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,This way, I'll be able to give the people\N in that town a chance to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:54.24,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We will cease hiding our movements\N and advance on the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.47,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,We will annihilate every city \Nwithin our reach along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.49,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Teach them the foolishness \Nof resisting Nazarick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:02.31,Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.11,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, \NPrincess Renner is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.57,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'll speak with her during dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.01,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,She said that if she can't \Nspeak with you immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.45,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,she'll begin yelling lies mixed with truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.08,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:56.55,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,But have the other two \Nwith her stand outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.71,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.47,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.22,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Is Father still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.23,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Do you think I'd kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.77,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.88,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Father is not well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.86,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having him rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:21.77,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is able to detain Father even \Nwithout Marquis Raeven's soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.89,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,That means that the head of the military
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.24,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,and the head of internal \Naffairs have taken your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.24,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Father planned to negotiate until the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.46,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,in order to minimize our losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.63,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I understand his feelings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.32,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,There had been no word of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.88,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,the Sorcerer Kingdom invading \Nsince the declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:46.76,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,But, in reality, his army has been \Nheading north this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.00,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,He took over the northern border \Nnear the Council State
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.39,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,in order to prevent them \Nfrom sending support troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.02,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:05:00.40,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,The invaded cities were completely destroyed \Nand all the people were massacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:02.40,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.53,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Please enlighten me with your brilliant mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:10.53,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,How have the Sorcerer Kingdom's \Nforces gone unnoticed until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.16,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,You've realized it yourself, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.48,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,It's the work of the people \Nin our own kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:22.30,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,But the only person who can keep \Nthis a secret so thoroughly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.05,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,...is Marquis Raeven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.22,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.72,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,This is Marquis Raeven's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:34.48,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,That man loves his son quite dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.88,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't he do it if his \Nson were taken hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.61,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,You think they're threatening him that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:45.86,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that he's decided that \Nthe royal family has no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.62,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,What action would you take \Nin a situation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.16,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,If things continue according \Nto the movements on this map,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.00,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,there will be a decisive battle \Nat the royal capital next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.00,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.75,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.63,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of winning or losing. \NWe have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:12.12,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,The Sorcerer Kingdom is burning down all the \Ncities and murdering all who live in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.92,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,We can only survive by \Ngathering all the soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.39,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,and risking everything on \Nthe slim chance of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.41,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the people, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.77,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,We'll advertise the cruelty of the \NSorcerer Kingdom and call them to arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:27.78,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you've truly become a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.41,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,Your way of thinking is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.16,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely useless in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.86,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,but a member of the royal family should \Nstand on the front lines to lead the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.76,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Father should take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.17,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,You can escape at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:50.47,Main,Renner,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. \NI'll do so when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.60,Main,Man 1,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.22,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joining! \NJust you wait, Sorcerer King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.56,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:02.02,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person needs to go to \Nsee the contents of the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.48,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys go and get a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:08.24,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Lakyus, is there a reason \Nwe can't go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.18,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:14.24,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,The Drop of Red are coming for \Nthis request, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.50,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't their leader, Mr. Azuth, your relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.12,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably have a lot to \Ncatch up on, right? I get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.88,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,So, you understand?! Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.88,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.56,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,So strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.13,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:30.13,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of request requires both \Nthe Drop of Red and Blue Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.38,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,It's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.01,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.01,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We shouldn't act separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.09,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,And we want to meet such a famous hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.40,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,He's a relative, so it wouldn't \Nhurt to meet him at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.86,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,This is the meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.25,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,Too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.10,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is definitely planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.03,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.58,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Um, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.24,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:07.42,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle's the type of person \Nthat makes most people grimace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.72,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lakyu! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:21.48,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle... Can't you dress a little \Nmore appropriately for this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:25.05,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now. At least we're not \Nhaving a meeting in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.65,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.86,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,It matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.09,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.95,Main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.79,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard he was a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.78,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.25,Main,Woman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:42.04,Main,Woman 2,0000,0000,0000,,A brat who doesn't even show her face \Nshouldn't act so high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.95,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Charm Person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.36,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way. Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.92,Main,Woman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.42,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Charm Person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.14,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.70,Main,Woman 2,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.03,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,Evileye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:02.94,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.43,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.44,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,You're on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.64,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:31.59,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last ones here and you're \Ngiving off such dangerous vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.84,Main,Eleventh Seat,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cocky for \Nbringing whores, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.84,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Hah. You're the ones who held \Na meeting in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.72,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to harass you guys a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.99,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.43,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,I would appreciate it if \Neveryone settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.35,Main,Eleventh Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Qua's the leader this time, \Nso I guess I'll listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.60,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:57.99,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Azuth Aindra and the other \Nabsent members from the Drop of Red...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.26,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,As well as all the members from Blue Rose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.82,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,We are here to scout you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.50,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Which country are you guys from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.75,Main,Eleventh Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.16,Main,Tina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:11.92,Main,Tia,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.75,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Please be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.39,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,If we really planned to kill all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:19.51,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't be wasting \Ntime introducing ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.22,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people from the Theocracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.60,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,The Theocracy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.60,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,The Theocracy's elite heroic unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.14,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Scripture, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.93,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,I heard one of you deviated \Nfrom the heroic path, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.84,Main,Tenth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:47.82,Main,Tenth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,But there are people here who are as \Nstrong as me, maybe even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.91,Main,Tenth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Evileye of the Blue Rose. \NYou'd be a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.29,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.65,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.91,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Theocracy's secret unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.68,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Want to work with us to fight \Nagainst the Sorcerer King?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.88,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.44,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your thoughts, Lord Azuth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.06,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,And what's the answer from the Blue Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.77,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,We won't force you by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:20.84,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to truly become our allies \Nand help secure the future of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.56,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse. How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.08,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just speak for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.17,Main,Gagaran,0000,0000,0000,,We all agree with Leader's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.08,Main,Tia/Tina/Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.50,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.78,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it'd be pointless\N to try to convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.01,Main,Fifth Seat,0000,0000,0000,,We hope everyone is able to bring \Nretribution upon the Sorcerer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.47,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.21,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.81,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here for the arrival \Nof the Sorcerer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.34,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely make his way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.06,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,You guys won't even be able to \Nget your swords close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.21,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:01.19,Main,Lakyus,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we can't leave the \Nroyal capital behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.60,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking me to join you, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.70,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be moving on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.64,Main,Evileye,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be able to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.84,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.02,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:19.46,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to escape, even if the \NSorcerer King surrounds the entire capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.22,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Welp, I'm going to unload \Na bit in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.82,Main,Azuth,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.82,Main,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! You took forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.57,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.73,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:49.37,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Ains, a representative is \Napproaching from the human army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:58.63,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I am the crown prince of the Re-Estize Kingdom, \NZanac Valleon Igana Ryle Vaiself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:02.56,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to speak with the Sorcerer King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.14,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wish to do, Lord Ains?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.85,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,I feel there's no need to listen, unless it's \Na messenger announcing the start of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:14.48,Main,Cocytus,0000,0000,0000,,If he refuses to converse with an opponent, \Nothers may think him close-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.35,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about a rumor when \Nno one is left to spread it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.49,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Albedo. Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.34,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,There may be someone watching from \Nafar who can speak ill of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.28,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:27.28,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Then, I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.52,Main,Cocytus,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Ains, bring guards with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.84,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,A royal came to me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.77,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,It is only right that I return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.88,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad to meet you, Sorcerer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:49.98,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zanac Valleon Igana Ryle Vaiself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.76,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad to meet you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.68,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Sorcerer King, Ains Ooal Gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.19,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Will water suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.48,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you very much, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.48,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:07.90,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the preparations for \Nour talk are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.10,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wish to speak about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.62,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I discuss why \Nour invasion is just?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:20.13,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, \Nthere's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:23.75,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing something this cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.74,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you accept our plea of surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.67,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Because there is no merit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.01,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Merit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:37.17,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,We will sacrifice your kingdom \Nto show the world that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:42.27,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,it is foolish to oppose \Nthe Sorcerer Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:47.03,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, we will enter your royal \Ncapital after decimating your forces
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.04,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,and turn everything into \Na mountain of rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.02,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave everything like that for \Nhundreds or even thousands of years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.88,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,In this way, stories about the folly \Nof going against the Sorcerer Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.86,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,will be passed down for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.13,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you chosen to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.63,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.53,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,There are other ways
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.57,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,to have Your Majesty's prestige \Nknown throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.98,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Why are your actions so close-minded?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:18.82,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Close-minded, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.42,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.76,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,My goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:35.45,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades from Yggdrasil may \Nexist somewhere in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.06,Italics,Momonga; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I had hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:42.12,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,My goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.93,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,It seems simple and complicated \Nat the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.35,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,My goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.63,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing I'm searching for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.88,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.89,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:16:01.27,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, isn't the ultimate \Ngoal of all creatures happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.77,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying it's fine to take away the \Nhappiness of others for the sake of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.52,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:10.69,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,If I can bring happiness \Nto the ones I treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about what \Nhappens to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.60,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,If your people could only achieve happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,by making the people of another \Ncountry suffer, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.67,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell your people \Nto give up on that happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.54,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,That logic is too extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.25,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.27,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.95,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:39.88,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,someone of Your Majesty's intelligence and \Npower had no other way to move forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.86,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,There may be other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:49.03,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's better to grab a hold of \Nthe chance to obtain such happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.15,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,if the opportunity to do \Nso is easily available.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.41,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "The goddess of \Nfortune is bald behind."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.47,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.89,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:03.10,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not belittling the gods \Nyou believe in or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.54,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.64,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.29,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.72,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:16.92,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you suffer for the happiness \Nof the people I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.43,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Does my answer satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.77,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say it is the \Nduty of those at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:28.81,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,to pursue benefits for their country \Nand bring happiness to their people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.89,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your reason for \Nrefusing our surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.82,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there is nothing else I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:39.47,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I guess it's my turn to question you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.20,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:45.71,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Who currently holds the sword \Nthat Gazef Stronoff wielded?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.48,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,The armor you're wearing was \Nalso previously worn by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.08,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:54.21,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,A man named Brain Unglaus is currently \Nin possession of that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.28,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Unglaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.47,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that man currently here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.35,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,No, he should be in the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.55,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:09.98,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it seems it doesn't matter what \Nspells I use to decimate your forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.47,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,We don't plan to lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:16.49,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you use magic that will \Nkill us without much suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.03,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.44,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,We've now become acquainted with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.62,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to kill \Nyou as gently as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:27.93,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.62,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,The drink was delicious, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:39.14,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you one last thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:45.52,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Did you or perhaps one of your \Nsubordinates kill my elder brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.56,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.31,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,The deed was probably done by one of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.02,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he's dead, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.44,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me know, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.95,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.51,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,A dauntless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.51,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,That must be what true royalty is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.20,Flashback,Ains; Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,My goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.73,Flashback,Ains; Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing I'm searching for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.84,Flashback,Ains; Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.82,Italics,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I was never fit to be a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:32.30,Italics,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make this \Nkingdom into a respectable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.36,Main,Nobles,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.75,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.36,Main,Noble B,0000,0000,0000,,What did the Sorcerer King say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:45.32,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,The Sorcerer King plans to \Nmassacre everyone in the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.87,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,There was no opportunity for negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.07,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.75,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like the talk didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:56.00,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the talk went as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.73,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.84,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of evil monster \Nwas the Sorcerer King?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.12,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,He was surprisingly human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.64,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.84,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was definitely \Na monster on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:11.21,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, he was the same as \Nany other human on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.53,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,So what is the plan of attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.15,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,There's no plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:22.02,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,We lost many of our commanders \Nand knights in the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.76,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:29.16,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like Stronoff, so I never thought \NI would miss him at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.07,Main,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,You people are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.17,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,King Zanac!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.92,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down! This is His Highness's tent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.08,Italics,Zanac; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,A rebellion at this point and time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.44,Italics,Zanac; Internal,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is just the result of \Ntheir desperate attempt to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.80,Main,Military Representative,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly people! Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.48,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.44,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason did you enter my tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.81,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, please surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.59,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.95,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,We can only survive if we \Ndefeat the Sorcerer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.28,Main,Noble B,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.82,Main,Noble C,0000,0000,0000,,He has an army of undead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.12,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,That may be the case for you, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:15.26,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll exchange your life for our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.83,Main,Noble C,0000,0000,0000,,We will go and pledge our \Nallegiance to the Sorcerer King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:22.34,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, please obey us quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:30.35,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the royal family, \NI have the resolve to fight to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.06,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Come, if you don't fear losing your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.69,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.22,Main,Zanac,0000,0000,0000,,Come and take this neck if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.05,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Ains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.32,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Albedo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:54.20,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,Some nobles from the Kingdom \Nwish to see the Sorcerer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.49,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:03.99,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,We are in awe of Your Majesty and \Nwish to bow down at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.22,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:21.48,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Bury him with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.49,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened to the \Narmor this man was wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:32.85,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? \NYou can't answer Lord Ains' question?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:35.18,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:38.12,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's with the \Nprince's corpse in his tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.63,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:44.38,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,You all did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.47,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I shall give you a reward \Ncomparable to your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:48.70,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.94,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare me and my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:54.39,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorcerer King! \NI pledge my complete allegiance to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.15,Main - Top,Noble B,0000,0000,0000,,I do, as well, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.93,Main,Noble C,0000,0000,0000,,Please show mercy on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:55.93,Main - Top,Noble D,0000,0000,0000,,Me, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.63,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:00.96,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will spare you and your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:02.65,Main,Nobles,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.78,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Albedo, send them to Neuronist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.65,Main,Albedo,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.06,Main,Noble A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:13.16,Main,Noble B,0000,0000,0000,,Long live His Majesty, the Sorcerer King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:14.02,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:15.41,Main,Aura,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Ains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:21.61,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to tell Neuronist not to \Nkill them unless they beg for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:23.67,Main,Aura,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Lord Ains!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:30.72,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they beg for death, \Ndon't kill them too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.50,Main,Aura,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.07,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:39.23,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,Cocytus will be the commander \Nand Mare the vice-commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.23,Main,Cocytus,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.23,Main,Mare,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:45.05,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,I allow the two of you to \Nfreely use your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:48.54,Main,Ains,0000,0000,0000,,So don't let a single one of them survive.
